<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM2.8">
<l>mālaiyuṟṟaka ṭaṟkiṭantavaṉ vaṇṭukiṇṭuna ṟuntuḻāy</l>
<l>mālaiyuṟṟava raipperuntiru mārvaṉaimalark kaṇṇaṉai</l>
<l>mālaiyuṟṟeḻun tāṭippāṭitti rintaraṅkaṉem māṉukkē</l>
<l>mālaiyuṟṟiṭun toṇṭarvāḻvukku mālaiyuṟṟateṉ ṉeñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Feeling love for</l>
<l rend="indent">Him with lotus-eyes, Him with a mountain[-like] large, sacred chest</l>
<l rend="indent">where a garland of fragrant sacred tulsi poked by bees dwells,</l>
<l rend="indent">Him who lay on the ocean that was agitated,</l>
<l>rising, dancing, singing [and] wandering,</l>
<l>the servants become mad solely on our Father, Raṅga -</l>
<l>My heart has felt desire for [their] happy lives.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
